FBIS4-19427 "drweu074_j_94011" FBIS-WEU-94-074 Daily Report 17 Apr 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Air Bases on Full Alert Air Bases on Full Alert LD1704124094 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1158 GMT 17 Apr 94 LD1704124094 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext Italian BFN [Text] Bosnian Serb forces are once more shelling the city of Gorazde, killing civilians. Meanwhile, Italian Defense Minister Fabio Fabbri has said: We have instructed our bases to move toward full alert status. Fabbri added that he did not rule out the possibility of going to Vicenza [north-east Italy] to make direct contact with the NATO command.
